{
  "page_title": "获取服务商凭证",
  "apis": [
    {
      "group_title": "获取服务商凭证",
      "api_name": "get_provider_token",
      "method": "POST",
      "api_url": "https://qyapi.weixin.qq.com/cgi-bin/service/get_provider_token",
      "description": "获取服务商凭证",
      "query_params": [],
      "body_params": [
        {
          "name": "corpid",
          "type": "string",
          "required": true,
          "description": "服务商的corpid"
        },
        {
          "name": "provider_secret",
          "type": "string",
          "required": true,
          "description": "服务商的secret，在服务商管理后台可见"
        }
      ],
      "response_params": [
        {
          "name": "provider_access_token",
          "type": "string",
          "required": false,
          "description": "服务商的access_token，最长为512字节"
        },
        {
          "name": "expires_in",
          "type": "uint32",
          "required": false,
          "description": "provider_access_token有效期（秒）"
        }
      ],
      "request_examples": [
        {
          "title": "请求示例",
          "language": "json",
          "code": "{\n    \"corpid\":\"xxxxx\",\n    \"provider_secret\":\"xxx\"\n}"
        }
      ],
      "response_examples": [
        {
          "title": "成功响应示例",
          "language": "json",
          "code": "{\n    \"provider_access_token\":\"enLSZ5xxxxxxJRL\",\n    \"expires_in\":7200\n}"
        }
      ],
      "sections": [
        {
          "title": "注意事项",
          "content": "开发者需要缓存provider_access_token，用于后续接口的调用（注意：不能频繁调用get_provider_token接口，否则会受到频率拦截）。当provider_access_token失效或过期时，需要重新获取。\nprovider_access_token的有效期通过返回的expires_in来传达，正常情况下为7200秒（2小时），有效期内重复获取返回相同结果，过期后获取会返回新的provider_access_token。\nprovider_access_token至少保留512字节的存储空间。\n企业微信可能会出于运营需要，提前使provider_access_token失效，开发者应实现provider_access_token失效时重新获取的逻辑。"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}